All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class GeocoderException
extends Exception

Defines exceptions that are thrown if something goes wrong while geocoding. GeocoderException is just a thin wrapper on top of the standard Excception class that allows for storing an error code if an error occured in the native code.
